{"tid":2139183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭榮鏗突辭任房委會職務","createTime":"2020-08-04T06:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T06:47:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"046e9ab32ac4e5e6033f12a2609aa28806476bc6","tid":2139183,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:26:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/OV2U44CCNOOD6YEGOJCWH7YDEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FOV2U44CCNOOD6YEGOJCWH7YDEI%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=92d1f93c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FOV2U44CCNOOD6YEGOJCWH7YDEI%2F&h=fbb20ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/OV2U44CCNOOD6YEGOJCWH7YDEI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗突辭任房委會職務<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wKOiVgAUzwDMEPBN_H-ET-YspSk=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JJ5HDFZ7PQRP6XAR5UIG6SRLKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwKOiVgAUzwDMEPBN_H-ET-YspSk%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJJ5HDFZ7PQRP6XAR5UIG6SRLKA.jpg&h=8058e6c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郭榮鏗已辭任房委會策劃小組委員會委員及建築小組委員會主席。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府上周宣佈押後立法會選舉前，大規模DQ多達12名民主派參選人，當中包括法律界立法會議員、公民黨郭榮鏗。根據房委會向委員發出的議事備忘錄，郭榮鏗已辭任房委會策劃小組委員會委員及建築小組委員會主席，上月31日起生效。郭榮鏗回覆查詢時稱「No comment（不予置評）」，未有交代辭任原因。<br />\n<br />\n現時房委會委員一般由行政長官委任，郭榮鏗在2015年獲委任為房委會委員，其後再度獲得委任，任期原定明年才結束。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗2012年循法律界晉身議會，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗早在立法會提名期開始後第二個工作天，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗回覆選舉主任時明言無意尋求外國制裁香港，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6cfbbd6657bcae95482aeb0401561554e952bb83","tid":2139183,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"認輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}